column4: NSLOCTEXT("[CD5C225448555222050A02B677D03D82]", "AD1EE074471DF401DF7127B3BE20E723", "I\'ve been looking around from the sky.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CD5C225448555222050A02B677D03D82]", "2EFDA3324149EFF5F7EABD9086EE5E51", "To the north, there\'s ice and snow. Living in such a cold place is crazy.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CD5C225448555222050A02B677D03D82]", "CB0D8F7C4EEC0FC4F43693B63A1582F1", "There\'s a small city made of iron to the west.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CD5C225448555222050A02B677D03D82]", "8D4E0F1E40E47A9D61758A8BD41D190E", "But the entrance and exit are closed. I can fly there.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CD5C225448555222050A02B677D03D82]", "A18D119E44E88BEBD6D624B78020A0F9", "There are groups of Digimon that have horns or claws.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CD5C225448555222050A02B677D03D82]", "6665D237497B5D1C95CBD78487BCF6F8", "I heard they make their homes by carving out wood.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CD5C225448555222050A02B677D03D82]", "23F922AB41722452BF42798A221A5168", "In the northwest is a forest with buildings.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CD5C225448555222050A02B677D03D82]", "DDB45DE749794917C8E4CDBBEC2CF0FD", "Have you been past the Great Canyon? It\'s like a maze.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CD5C225448555222050A02B677D03D82]", "E9C0E01F429704F8A4F12D90D2348697", "I can\'t see the middle of the island. I see only clouds.")
